article.description: — Emmanuel Bandoumel had a career-high 23 points as SMU beat East Carolina 80-66 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Bandoumel scores 23 to lift SMU past East Carolina 80-66
article.linkText: Bandoumel scores 23 to lift SMU past East Carolina 80-66
article.story: GREENVILLE, N.C. -- — Emmanuel Bandoumel had a career-high 23 points as SMU beat East Carolina 80-66 on Saturday night. Michael Weathers had 13 points for SMU (18-5, 9-2 American Athletic Conference). Marcus Weathers added 11 points. Zach Nutall had 10 points. Kendric Davis, the Mustangs' leading scorer at 20 points per game, had 7 points. Tristen Newton had 19 points for the Pirates (12-12, 3-9). Brandon Suggs added 14 points and eight rebounds. Ludgy Debaut had 11 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
